{"word":"παχύνω","slug":"παχύνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παχύνω</el></b> [<el>παχύς</el> ‘thick’ <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fr.\">fr.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πήγνυμι\">πήγνυμι</a></el> in sense of making liquids stiff] <b>make fat,</b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> and in imagery in citation of <a href='B:290 6:10'>Isaiah 6:10</a> become dull <b><a href='B:470 13:15'>Mt 13:15</a>; <a href='B:510 28:27'>Ac 28:27</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Πάφος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πέδη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}